cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY 

This paper discusses the use of a recurrent neural network for estimating dynamics in a robotic pouring task. This task falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of a LSTM recurrent neural network also suggests the paper could fall under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the discussion of data collection and preprocessing suggests the paper could also fall under the category of systems and control (cs.SY).
